premise_source_doc_sentence: Meghan Marguerite McCain  (  born October 23 , 1984  )  is an American columnist , author , Fox News host and contributor , and blogger .
She is the daughter of 2008 presidential nominee and long-time U.S. Senator John McCain and Cindy Hensley McCain .
McCain first received media attention in 2007 for her blog , McCain Blogette , on which she documented life on the campaign trail and mused about fashion , music , and pop culture .
In 2009 , she became a contributing author for The Daily Beast , and in 2011 , began appearing as a contributor on MSNBC .
In 2013 , she began hosting on the start-up Pivot channel and in 2014 assumed the co-host role on Pivot 's TakePart Live until that show was canceled later in the year .
In July 2015 , McCain joined Premiere Networks as host of the nationally syndicated radio program America Now .
McCain also signed on as a FOX News contributor in July 2015 , and was officially named a regular co-host of the afternoon talk program Outnumbered on November 14 , 2016 .
Meghan McCain is the daughter of Republican U.S. Senator John McCain of Arizona .
Dirty Sexy Politics is a 2010 political memoir written by Meghan McCain , the daughter of Republican Senator John McCain , about the 2008 United States presidential election .
